        <abstract> 
<p>Sends his paper on "Natural science and morality", notwithstanding CD’s disinclination for the subject. This work parallels H. Spencer’s in the <hi rend="italic">Data of ethics</hi> [1879].</p> 
            <p>Clerk Maxwell and William Thomson have encouraged his work in physics; STP looks for CD’s support on evolution.</p>
        </abstract>
